Paramo Says ECB Will Ensure Inflation Expectations Are Anchored

-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 
2011-09-19T14:08:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/paramo-says-ecb-will-ensure-inflation-expectations-are-anchored.html
European Central Bank Executive
Board member Jose Manuel Gonzalez-Paramo said the bank is
focussed on anchoring inflation expectations.  “A central bank with a mandate has to deliver on its
mandate,” which is to achieve price stability, Gonzalez-Paramo
said at an event in  Frankfurt  today. “We need a proper
anchoring of inflation expectations.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
 jrandow@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Matthew Brockett at 
 mbrockett1@bloomberg.net  